### [1] Rider 회원가입
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "rider1@delivery-msa.com",
  "password": "rider1111",
  "name": "라이더",
  "phone": "010-4444-4444",
  "role": "RIDER"
}

### [2] Rider 로그인
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "rider1@delivery-msa.com",
  "password": "rider1111"
}

### [3] 배달 가능한 주문 목록 조회 (owner가 READY_FOR_PICKUP 처리 후 나타남)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/deliveries/available
Authorization: Bearer <RIDER_ACCESS_TOKEN>

### [4] 배달 수락 (orderId는 [3] 응답에서 복사)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/deliveries/accept/<ORDER_ID>
Authorization: Bearer <RIDER_ACCESS_TOKEN>

### [5] 현재 위치 업데이트
POST http://localhost:8080/api/deliveries/location
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <RIDER_ACCESS_TOKEN>

{
  "latitude": 37.4980,
  "longitude": 127.0276
}

### [6] 음식 픽업 완료 (deliveryId는 [4] 응답에서 복사)
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/deliveries/<DELIVERY_ID>/pickup
Authorization: Bearer <RIDER_ACCESS_TOKEN>

### [7] 배달 완료
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/deliveries/<DELIVERY_ID>/complete
Authorization: Bearer <RIDER_ACCESS_TOKEN>

### [8] 내 배달 이력
GET http://localhost:8080/api/deliveries/my
Authorization: Bearer <RIDER_ACCESS_TOKEN>

### [9] 내 알림 목록 (배달 배정/픽업/완료 이벤트 확인용)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/notifications
Authorization: Bearer <RIDER_ACCESS_TOKEN>
